OL,6,FA in a viscous attack refused to
OL,7,Fattend court as he was jailed for life.
OL,9,FAustin Duckworth, 37, must serve at
OL,10,Fleast 17 years before being able to
OL,11,Fapply for parole.
OL,13,FPreston Crown Court was told he
OL,14,Fvisited his father Stephen, 72, in
OL,15,FAugust last year demanding a pair of
OL,16,Fwalking boots.
OL,18,FWhen his father said he could not find
OL,19,Fthe boots, Duckworth, who had suffered
OL,20,Fdeclining mental health, kicked down a
OL,21,Fdoor and punched his father in the jaw.
