OL,3,CSon who killed his own father refuses
OL,4,Cto attend court as he's jailed for life
OL,6,FThe pensioner, who had a number of pre-
OL,7,Fexisting health conditions, fell to
OL,8,Fhis knees and tried to defend himself
OL,9,Fas his son "pummelled him" in the
OL,10,Fhallway of the house.
OL,12,FAustin Duckworth then left the house
OL,13,Fbut when the police arrived at the
OL,14,Fhouse, his father was able to give a
OL,15,Fstatement about what happened.
OL,17,FTragically, Mr Duckworth told officers
OL,18,Fhis son "used to be a son to be proud
OL,19,Fof".
