OL,3,CSon who killed his own father refuses
OL,4,Cto attend court as he's jailed for life
OL,6,FThe pair had previously enjoyed a
OL,7,Fclose relationship and Mr Duckworth
OL,8,Fhad left his entire estate to his son
OL,9,Fin his will.JMr Duckworth, unaware
OL,10,Fthat he suffered a severe injury to
OL,11,Fhis brain, declined to attend hospital.
OL,13,FHe was later transferred to where he
OL,14,Fdied on 12 October 2023.
OL,16,FJudge Medland said Duckworth's
OL,17,Fconviction for murder was on the basis
OL,18,Fhe aimed to seriously harm his father,
OL,19,Fbut did not intend to kill.
