OL,3,CSon who killed his own father refuses
OL,4,Cto attend court as he's jailed for life
OL,6,FHe said: "The defendant is not present
OL,7,Ftoday for the sentence hearing. He has
OL,8,Frefused to attend.J"That is, in my
OL,9,Fjudgement, an act of contempt to the
OL,10,Fmemory of Stephen Duckworth, the wider
OL,11,Ffamily and the court. It displays a
OL,12,Ftotal absence of remorse.J"This was
OL,13,Fthe culmination of a period of about
OL,14,Fthree years or slightly more during
OL,15,Fwhich Austin Duckworth's behaviour was
OL,16,Ffrequently unacceptable, aggressive,
OL,17,Fthreatening and deeply, deeply
OL,18,Ftroubling."
