OL,6,FJudge Medland KC said bizarre and
OL,7,Fabusive messages and social media
OL,8,Framblings, in which Duckworth offered
OL,9,F#5,000 to anyone prepared to kill his
OL,10,Ffather showed signs of poor mental
OL,11,Fhealth.JHe said the offence was
OL,12,Faggravated by the elder Mr Duckworth's
OL,13,Fvulnerability, and the fact it had
OL,14,Ftaken place in his own home.
OL,16,FIn mitigation he took into account
OL,17,FDuckworth's previous good character
OL,18,Fand his mental health difficulties.
